event manager environment CERTBOT-APPID certbot

event manager applet START-CERTBOT
 event timer cron cron-entry "0 4 * * *"
 action 1.0 syslog msg "Applet: START-CERTBOT Checking if certificate requires renewal"
 action 2.0 cli command "enable"
 action 3.0 cli command "app-hosting start appid $_CERTBOT-APPID"
